https://newsfilter.io/a/887be2a2de3f0131b010ffcce8f6f35f

links.title: Netflix Price Increases Get Thumbs Up From Wall Street Bulls
links.description: One of the biggest bargains in consumer entertainment just got a little more expensive. (ticker: NFLX) on Thursday announced a price increas e for U.S. subscribers. The price of a standard Netflix plan climbs by $1 a month to $13.99, from $12.99. The price for premium plans jumps by $2 a month to $17.99 from $15.99.
